f%20an%20%26quot%3Baccountability%20sink.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEconomist%20Dan%20Davies%20uses%20the%20term%20to%20describe%20how%20companies%20avoid%20responsibility%20by%20deferring%20decisions%20to%20algorithms.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDavies%20says%20customer%20feedback%20is%20often%20ignored%20when%20tech%20is%20accountable%20for%20decisions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20one%20of%20every%20traveler's%20worst%20nightmares%3A%20You%20arrive%20at%20the%20boarding%20gate%20to%20be%20told%20your%20flight%20is%20overbooked%20and%20you've%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-do-if-airline-bumps-you-from-overbooked-flight-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebumped%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20complain%20at%20the%20counter%20%E2%80%94%20you%20have%20an%20important%20business%20meeting%20or%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20miss%20your%20friend's%20wedding.%20Can't%20they%20bump%20someone%20else%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-people-should-never-do-on-airplanes-flight-attendant-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eattendant%3C%2Fa%3E%20tells%20you%20there's%20nothing%20they%20can%20do%20to%20help.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-and-worst-airlines-us-canada-customer-satisfaction-delta-southwest-2024-5%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSouthwest%2520Airlines%2520took%2520top%2520honors%2Cthree%2520spots%2520from%2520last%2520year.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECompany%3C%2Fa%3E%20policy%20is%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20frustrating%2C%20the%20gate%20attendant%20is%20not%20at%20fault%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20the%20whole%20point.%20Companies%20create%20algorithms%20to%20decide%20who%20is%20bumped%20from%20a%20flight%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20system's%20decision%20is%20final%20and%20no%20one%20employee%20is%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20an%20example%20of%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhat%20economist%20Dan%20Davies%20calls%20an%20%26quot%3Baccountability%20sink%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20new%20book%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Db89b4850e05bd4939f2d9e7a8caa9cc0c31a3471114ff89757b06b527d0810cd%26postID%3D668d8a0b7d643e28300bcef5%26postSlug%3Dflight-refunds-customer-service-accountability-sinks-dan-davies-2024-7%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FUnaccountability-Machine-Systems-Terrible-Decisions-ebook%252Fdp%252FB0CGFWBFD6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Unaccountability%20Machine%3A%20Why%20Big%20Systems%20Make%20Terrible%20Decisions%20%E2%80%94%20and%20How%20the%20World%20Lost%20its%20Mind.%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorporations%20absolve%20their%20employees%20of%20responsibility%20by%20delegating%20decision-making%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fforget-ai-algorithm-apocalypse-driving-humans-lives-data-stock-market-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealgorithm%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20deferring%20to%20company%20policy.%20No%20one%20person%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20empowered%20to%20make%20a%20judgment%20call%2C%20and%20the%20customer's%20frustrations%20are%20moot.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIt's%20not%20just%20at%20airlines%3B%20technology%20and%20an%20increased%20focus%20on%20streamlining%20processes%20to%20cut%20costs%20have%20allowed%20companies%20in%20all%20kinds%20of%20industries%20to%20create%20accountability%20sinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavies%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20once%20a%20decision%20like%20bumping%20someone%20from%20a%20flight%20is%20made%2C%20%26quot%3Bthen%20it's%20just%20natural%20to%20create%20an%20accountability%20sink.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20want%20any%20accountability%20there%20because%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20have%20pressure%20put%20on%20anyone%20to%20change%20the%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20Davies%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20technology%20can%20optimize%20decision-making%20processes%2C%20it%20can%20also%20prevent%20customers%20from%20reaching%20someone%20with%20the%20power%20to%20make%20a%20decision%20that%20strays%20from%20the%20corporate%20script.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20the%20sympathetic%20gate%20attendant%20telling%20the%20disgruntled%20customer%2C%20%26quot%3B'We've%20got%20a%20policy%2C%20there's%20nothing%20that%20can%20be%20done%2C'%26quot%3B%20Davies%20said%2C%20the%20customer's%20negative%20emotions%20are%20ignored%20and%20poured%20into%20a%20void%20%E2%80%94%20or%20an%20accountability%20sink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20situation%20that%20people%20find%20so%20incredibly%20frustrating%2C%26quot%3B%20Davies%20said.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20it's%20bad%20to%20have%20decisions%20go%20against%20you%2C%20but%20it's%20absolutely%20psychologically%20intolerable%20to%20feel%20like%20you're%20not%20being%20listened%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c8302fe0-a4b6-458a-b9d4-856b4b4c93cb%5C%22%3ESorry%2C%20it's%20company%20policy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Davies%2C%20accountability%20sinks%20emerged%20over%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20past%20decades%20of%20privatization%20and%20technological%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201980s%2C%20he%20said%2C%20free-market%20capitalism%20and%20profit%20maximization%20became%20the%20norm%2C%20spearheaded%20by%20economist%20Milton%20Friedman%20and%20championed%20by%20Ronald%20Reagan%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Margaret%20Thatcher%20in%20the%20UK.%20Since%20then%2C%20companies%20have%20focused%20on%20profits%2C%20growth%2C%20and%20maximizing%20shareholder%20value%2C%20according%20to%20Davies%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20has%20created%20accountability%20sinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20technology%20boom%20of%20the%201990s%2C%20Davies%20said%20companies%20developed%20computer%20systems%20to%20make%20decisions%20for%20them%20because%20of%20the%20volume%20and%20complexity%20of%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20middle%20management%20and%20customer%20service%20jobs%20were%20cut%20or%20outsourced%20as%20corporations%20prioritized%20profits%2C%20optimizing%20costs%2C%20and%20delivering%20strong%20quarterly%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20big%20problem%20with%20cutting%20the%20feedback%20link%20is%20that%20you're%20cutting%20off%20all%20of%20your%20own%20sources%20of%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20Davies%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20your%20customers%20can%20be%20getting%20steadily%20more%20and%20more%20annoyed%20with%20you%2C%20and%20you%20won't%20really%20know%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20the%20person%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20Davies%20said%20ideally%2C%20any%20customer%20bumped%20from%20a%20flight%20should%20be%20able%20to%20talk%20directly%20with%20an%20employee%20with%20some%20level%20of%20decision-making%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20answer%20is%20usually%20there%20are%20no%20more%20flights%20going%2C%20and%20there's%20nothing%20that%20can%20be%20done%2C%20but%20just%20simply%20having%20that%20experience%20of%20someone%20listening%20to%20you%2C%20in%20my%20view%2C%20is%20just%20really%2C%20really%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20accountability%20sinks%20aren't%20just%20at%20the%20boarding%20gate.%20You%20may%20have%20experienced%20similar%20frustrations%20when%20calling%20your%20internet%20or%20cellphone%20provider%2C%20bank%2C%20or%20credit%20card%20company.%20It%20often%20looks%20like%20a%20customer%20service%20representative%20working%20within%20a%20system%20with%20limited%20options%20to%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccountability%20sinks%20can%20range%20from%20customer%20service%20to%20decision-making%20at%20major%20corporations.%20According%20to%20Davies%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-to-plead-guilty-isnt-out-woods-yet-government-contracts-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoeing%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20company%20rife%20with%20accountability%20sinks.%20The%20airline%20manufacturer%20is%20at%20the%20center%20of%20legal%20troubles%20stemming%20from%20two%20deadly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-crashes-groundings-timeline-737-max-777-air-force-tanker-2024-1%23737-max-crashes-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecrashes%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202018%20and%202019%2C%20and%20an%20incident%20in%20January%20when%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffbi-tells-boeing-737-blowout-passengers-may-be-victims-crime-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoeing%20737%20Max's%3C%2Fa%3E%20door%20plug%20came%20off%20mid-flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavies%20said%20decision-makers%20at%20Boeing%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehave%20been%20too%20focused%20on%20share%20buybacks%20and%20optimizing%20costs%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20recent%20years%20while%20accountability%20sinks%20developed%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-disaster-american-businesses-greedy-broken-stock-market-wall-street-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanufacturing%3C%2Fa%3E%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20when%20Boeing%20CEO%20Dave%20Calhoun%20announced%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-dave-calhoun-failed-to-turn-boeing-around-737-max-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresignation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20told%20CNBC%20that%20Boeing%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bbad%20habit%26quot%3B%20of%20focusing%20too%20much%20on%20delivery%20time%2C%20which%20might%20have%20given%20the%20message%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20movement%20of%20the%20airplane%20is%20more%20important%20than%20the%20first-time%20quality%20of%20the%20product.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20Davies%20said%20accountability%20sinks%20will%20eventually%20catch%20up%20with%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20time%2C%20it%20degrades%20the%20brand%2C%20and%20the%20resentment%20builds%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAt%20some%20point%2C%20there's%20just%20going%20to%20be%20this%20huge%20bump%20where%20you%20get%20back%20to%20reality%2C%20and%20all%20of%20the%20accountability%20you've%20been%20pouring%20into%20this%20sink%20for%20the%20last%2010%20years%20comes%20back%20and%20hits%20you%20in%20one%20massive%20lump.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20see%20accountability%20sinks%20elsewhere%20in%20life%3F%20This%20reporter%20wants%20to%20hear%20from%20you.%20Please%20reach%20out%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajtowfighi%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ejtowfighi%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflight-refunds-customer-service-accountability-sinks-dan-davies-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720863423000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669047318893442a5155ecc8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflight-refunds-customer-service-accountability-sinks-dan-davies-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20you've%20ever%20been%20at%20your%20wit's%20end%20with%20a%20customer%20service%20rep%20who%20can't%20help%2C%20you%20may%20be%20a%20victim%20of%20an%20%26quot%3Baccountability%20sink.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jtowfighi%40insider.com%20(John%20Towfighi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflight-refunds-customer-service-accountability-sinks-dan-davies-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kareena%20swoons%20over%20Radhika's%20bridal%20look%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720863406000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111709236%2Cimgsize-85776.cms%22%2C%22or