nal%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-leading-biden-rnc-convention-polls-election-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720863122000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669160629caa6ed01e012b14%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-leading-biden-rnc-convention-polls-election-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20has%20his%20best%20standing%20ever%20in%20a%20presidential%20race%20even%20as%20he's%20held%20few%20public%20events%20since%20Joe%20Biden's%20disastroushttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-vice-president-nominee-candidates-2024-1%20debate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-leading-biden-rnc-convention-polls-election-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Satellite%20Images%20Indicate%20Huge%20Architectural%20Wealth%20Under%20Bodh%20Gaya%20Temple%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20geospatial%20analysis%20utilising%20satellite%20images%20and%20ground%20surveys%20has%20found%20evidence%20of%20the%20presence%20of%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20architectural%20wealth%26quot%3B%20buried%20in%20the%20Mahabodhi%20temple%20complex%20and%20its%20surroundings%20in%20Bihar's%20Bodh%20Gaya%2C%20officials%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20has%20been%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20Bihar%20Heritage%20Development%20Society%20(BHDS)%2C%20a%20wing%20of%20the%20Art%2C%20Culture%20and%20Youth%20Department%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Cardiff%20University%20of%20the%20United%20Kingdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mahabodhi%20temple%20complex%2C%20a%20UNESCO%20World%20Heritage%20site%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20four%20holy%20areas%20related%20to%20the%20life%20of%20Lord%20Gautam%20Buddha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBodh%20Gaya%20is%20a%20place%20where%20Lord%20Buddha%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20attained%20enlightenment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20study%20has%20unearthed%20evidence%20of%20the%20presence%20of%20archaeological%20treasure%20beneath%20the%20soil%20of%20the%20UNESCO%20World%20Heritage%20site%20and%20its%20surrounding%20areas.%20It's%20a%20huge%20architectural%20wealth%20that%20needs%20further%20excavation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Art%2C%20Culture%20and%20Youth%20Department's%20Additional%20Chief%20Secretary%20Harjot%20Kaur%20Bamhrah%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UK-based%20varsity%20and%20the%20BHDS%20are%20cooperating%20in%20the%20project%2C%20'Archaeology%20on%20the%20footsteps%20of%20the%20Chinese%20traveller%20Xuanzang'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengaluru-based%20National%20Institute%20of%20Advanced%20Studies%20faculty%20member%20MB%20Rajni%2C%20one%20of%20the%20project%20members%2C%20studied%20satellite%20images%20of%20the%20Mahabodhi%20temple%20and%20its%20surroundings%20and%20tried%20to%20correlate%20the%20findings%20with%20the%20description%20of%20'Xuanzang'%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20present%20Mahabodhi%20temple%20complex%20at%20Bodh%20Gaya%20comprises%20the%2050-metre-high%20grand%20temple%2C%20the%20Vajrasana%2C%20the%20sacred%20Bodhi%20tree%20and%20other%20six%20sacred%20sites%20of%20Buddha's%20enlightenment%2C%20surrounded%20by%20numerous%20ancient%20stupas%2C%20well%20maintained%20and%20protected%20by%20inner%2C%20middle%20and%20outer%20circular%20boundaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BHDS%20in%20association%20with%20Cardiff%20University%20has%20been%20working%20on%20the%20multidisciplinary%20project%20on%20the%20archaeological%20trail%20of%20the%20travel%20of%207th-century%20Chinese%20translator%20monk%2C%20Xuanzang%2C%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20satellite%20images%20from%20the%20last%20several%20years%20show%20an%20alignment%20of%20structures%20to%20the%20north%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20buried%20underground%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bamhrah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20the%20images%20show%20the%20shift%20of%20the%20river%20Niranjana%20from%20east%20to%20west.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20us%20remember%20that%20the%20Mahabodhi%20temple%20is%20west%20of%20the%20river%2C%20and%20the%20Sujata%20Stupa%20and%20several%20other%20archaeological%20remains%20are%20located%20east%20of%20the%20river.%20The%20monuments%20and%20other%20archaeological%20remains%20in%20the%20east%20of%20the%20river%20are%20now%20regarded%20to%20be%20independent%20of%20the%20Mahabodhi%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20latest%20finding%20shows%20that%20both%20the%20temple%20and%20the%20Sujata%20stupa%20along%20with%20other%20archaeological%20remains%20stood%20on%20the%20same%20river%20bank%20in%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBamhrah%20said%20this%20is%20really%20%26quot%3Bvery%20significant%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThus%2C%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20possibility%20that%20the%20monuments%20and%20other%20archaeological%20remains%2C%20now%20east%20of%20the%20river%2C%20were%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Mahabodhi%20complex%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BHDS%20plans%20to%20start%20%26quot%3Bresearch%20to%20delimit%20the%20boundaries%20of%20the%20Mahabodhi%20complex%20in%20the%20light%20of%20these%20findings%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFresh%20ground-penetrating%20radar%20(GPR)%20survey%2C%20followed%20by%20excavations%2C%20will%20be%20undertaken%20to%20unravel%20the%20buried%20archaeological%20features%20shown%20by%20satellite%20images%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20findings%2C%20BHDS%20Executive%20Director%20Bijoy%20Kumar%20Choudhary%20told%20PTI%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20fresh%20study%20has%20revealed%20several%20findings%20that%20include%20to%20the%20north%20of%20the%20temple%20premises%2C%20a%20square%20monastery%20complex%20enclosed%20by%20a%20wall%20with%20a%20surrounding%20moat%20and%20an%20extended%20settlement%20to%20its%20north%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHiuen%20Tsang%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Xuanzang%2C%20was%20a%20Chinese%20Buddhist%2C%20monk%20scholar%2C%20traveller%20and%20translator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20travelled%20from%20China%20to%20India%20to%20obtain%20Buddhist%20scriptures%20during%20the%20reign%20of%20King%20Harsha%20Vardhan.%20He%20is%20best%20known%20for%20his%20journey%20to%20India%20from%20629%20to%20645%20CE%20and%20his%20efforts%20to%20bring%20over%20657%20Indian%20texts%20into%20China.%20His%20writings%20had%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20the%20development%20of%20Buddhism%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EXuanzang's%20travelogue%20of%20India%20helped%20Alexander%20Cunningham%20in%201860s%20and%201870s%20to%20identify%20famous%20sites%20such%20as%20Nalanda%20and%20Vaishali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20square%20wall%20of%20the%20monastery%20complex%20is%20of%20special%20interest%20as%20it%20had%20been%20excavated%20by%20Cunningham%20in%20the%2019th%20century%2C%20but%20no%20further%20excavations%20have%20been%20conducted.%20However%2C%20this%20area%20has%20great%20potential%20for%20systematic%20excavation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUpon%20analysing%20satellite%20imagery%2C%20we%20identified%20two%20concentric%20squares%E2%80%A6an%20outer%20square%20enclosing%204.9%20acres%20and%20an%20inner%20one%20enclosing%202.5%20acres.%20Between%20the%20outer%20and%20inner%20squares%2C%20there%20is%20a%20gap%20of%20about%2015%20metres%20and%20in%20the%20south%20and%2020%20meters%20in%20the%20east%20and%20the%20west.%20The%20southern%20boundary%20of%20the%20outer%20square%20is%20approximately%20300%20feet%20from%20the%20wall%20of%20the%20Mahabodhi%20temple%20complex%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20the%20report%20of%20Rajni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20traces%20of%20the%20monastery%20are%20no%20longer%20visible%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20satellite%20imagery%20revealed%20that%20the%20squares%20overlap%20significantly%20with%20Samanvay%20Ashram%2C%26quot%3B%20Rajni%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20particular%2C%20the%20well%20that%20Cunningham%20observed%20at%20the%20Centre%20of%20the%20monastery's%20pillared%20court%20might%20be%20one%20of%20the%20two%20wells%20located%20within%20the%20Ashram%20to%20the%20south%20of%20the%20statue%20of%20Dwarkoji%20Sunderani%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Ashram's%20southern%20boundary%2C%20marked%20by%20a%20compound%20wall%20on%20a%20raised%20ridge%2C%20aligns%20with%20the%20southern%20boundary%20of%20the%20outer%20square%2C%20thus%20suggesting%20the%20buried%20remnants%20of%20an%20earlier%20wall%2C%26quot%3B%20Rajni%20added.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720862880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fdbsgvelc_mahabodhi-temple-bodh-gaya-ani_625x300_13_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsatellite-images-indicate-huge-architectural-wealth-under-bodh-gayas-mahabodhi-temple-report-6096670%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20geospatial%20analysis%20utilising%20satellite%20images%20and%20ground%20surveys%20has%20found%20evidence%20of%20the%20presence%20of%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20architectural%20wealth%26quot%3B%20buried%20in%20the%20Mahabodhi%20temple%20complex%20and%20its%20surroundings%20in%20Bihar's%20Bodh%20Gaya%2C%20officials%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsatellite-images-indicate-huge-architectural-wealth-under-bodh-gayas-mahabodhi-temple-report-6096670%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsatellite-images-indicate-huge-architectural-wealth-under-bodh-gayas-mahabodhi-temple-report-6096670%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsatellite-images-indicate-huge-architectural-wealth-under-bodh-gayas-mahabodhi-temple-report-6096670%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20key%20to%20earning%20more%20money%2C%20switching%20careers%2C%20and%20getting%20sober%20for%20this%20millennial%3A%20going%20back%20to%20college%20at%2032%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223845%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Erin%20Vaughan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668e841839de72f47bc9ebcd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222884%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EErin%20Vaughan%20went%20back%20to%20school%20at%2032%20and%20found%20a%20new%20career.%20%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Erin%20Vaughan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EErin%20Vaughan%2C%2041%2C%20went%20back%20to%20college%20when%20she%20was%2032.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20allowed%20her%20to%20find%20a%20new%20career%20path%20she%20wouldn't%20have%20considered%20otherwise.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20was%20challenging%20to%20get%20a%20degree%20later%20in%20life%2C%20but%20she%20said%20it%20was%20well%20worth%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20an%20exaggeration%20to%20say%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-xer-why-going-back-school-50s-was-worth-it-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egoing%20back%20to%20school%3C%2Fa%3E%20changed%20Erin%20Vaughan's%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVaughan%2C%2041%2C%20completed%20two%20semesters%20of%20college%20in%20her%20mid-twenties%2C%20but%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-repayment-issues-debt-relief-broken-industry-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewasn't%20able%20to%20afford%20to%20further%20her%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20time%2C%20so%20she%20dropped%20out%20and%20began%20pursuing%20her%20passion%20for%20the%20culinary%20field.%20She%20moved%20to%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20worked%20in%20restaurants%2C%20and%20started%20her%20own%20business%20as%20a%20personal%20chef%20%E2%80%94%20and%20she%20said%20she%20loved%20working%20with%20her%20clients%2C%20who%20were%20primarily%20older%20adults%20who%20needed%20nutritional%20meals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20given%20her%20older%20client%20base%2C%20Vaughan%20wanted%20to%20further%20her%20knowledge%20of%20nutrition.%20At%20the%20age%20of%2032%2C%20she%20went%20back%20to%20school%20and%20graduated%20in%202020%20with%20a%20bachelor%20of%20science%20degree%20in%20food%20science%20and%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20to%20take%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstories-of-student-loan-debt-hamster-wheel-borrowers-cant-escape-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2420%2C000%20in%20student%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20afford%20the%20program%2C%20but%20she%20said%20it%20was%20well%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20truly%20one%20of%20the%20hardest%20things%20I've%20ever%20done%2C%20but%20the%20most%20rewarding%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Vaughan%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20changed%20how%20I%20think%20about%20myself.%20It%20has%20changed%20how%20I%20think%20about%20my%20abilities.%20It%20has%20definitely%20changed%20my%20career.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20restaurant%20industry%20had%20a%20heavy%20drinking%20culture%2C%20Vaughan%20said%2C%20and%20once%20she%20started%20school%20and%20grew%20committed%20to%20the%20program%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20become%20sober.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20biggest%20thing%20I've%20ever%20done%20for%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20four%20years%20where%20I've%20worked%20toward%20one%20goal%2C%20and%20it%20empowered%20every%20aspect%20of%20my%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVaughan%20now%20works%20as%20a%20project%20manager%20for%20quality%20assurance%20at%20a%20men's%20personal%20care%20brand.%20According%20to%20documents%20reviewed%20by%20BI%2C%20she's%20already%20received%20a%20series%20of%20promotions%20at%20the%20company%20that%20have%20boosted%20her%20paychecks%20by%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20per%20month.%20She%20said%20it's%20a%20role%20where%20she%20feels%20like%20she%20can%20bring%20a%20lot%20of%20value%20and%20continue%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20among%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-going-back-to-school-college-degree-career-advancement-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrowing%20number%20of%20older%20adults%20who%20have%20decided%20to%20return%20to%20school%3C%2Fa%3E%20later%20in%20life%20to%20give%20themselves%20another%20shot%20at%20higher%20education.%20A%20recent%20paper%20from%20the%20National%20Bureau%20of%20Economic%20Research%20found%20that%20about%2070%25%20of%20the%20rise%20in%20college%20completion%20from%201990%20to%202010%20is%20a%20result%20of%20the%20growing%20share%20of%20adults%20getting%20degrees%20after%20their%20mid-twenties.%20On%20top%20of%20that%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gallup.com%2Fanalytics%2F644939%2Fstate-of-higher-education.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Gallup%20and%20the%20Lumina%20Foundation%20on%20the%20state%20of%20higher%20education%20in%202024%20found%20that%20%26quot%3Badults'%20interest%20in%20pursuing%20some%20form%20of%20higher%20education%20is%20at%20the%20highest%20level%26quot%3B%20the%20organizations%20ever%20recorded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20back%20to%20school%20opened%20Vaughan's%20eyes%20to%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20different%20career%20path%2C%20and%20she%20now%20has%20a%20steady%20job%2C%20bigger%20paychecks%2C%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20fulfillment%20with%20the%20opportunities%20her%20degree%20opened%20up%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20that%20inkling%2C%20do%20it.%20It%20will%20be%20rewarding%2C%26quot%3B%20Vaughan%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt'll%20be%20hard%2C%20but%20it's%20kind%20like%2C%20you%20don't%20enjoy%20doing%20squats.%20You%20enjoy%20it%20afterward.%20You%20enjoy%20the%20results.%20And%20I%20think%20anybody%20who's%20in%20their%20head%20about%20going%20back%2C%20the%20only%20way%20to%20move%20through%20that%20is%20actually%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f3ee4796-bcc3-4bcb-a140-b10f908d99c7%5C%22%3E'It's%20opened%20up%20a%20world%20of%20potential'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20back%20to%20school%20hasn't%20made%20things%20perfect%20for%20Vaughan.%20Graduating%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20Vaughan%20said%20she%20had%20to%20accept%20a%20job%20with%20a%20very%20low%20salary%20because%20she%20had%20no%20other%20option%2C%20and%20she%20went%20through%20three%20different%20jobs%20in%20search%20of%20better%20pay%20before%20landing%20her%20current%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20few%20years%20of%20instability%20set%20her%20up%20for%20a%20steady%20future%20where%20she%20can%20look%20toward%20achieving%20her%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20shine%20in%20my%20job%2C%20and%20I%20know%20that%20I%20can%20use%20the%20skills%20I%20have%20in%20the%20future%20and%20blaze%20my%20own%20trail%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20opened%20up%20a%20world%20of%20potential%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20going%20to%20school%20later%20in%20life%20doesn't%20always%20pay%20off.%20BI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-xer-college-degree-cant-find-job-government-student-debt-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20spoke%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20Gen%20Xer%20who%20pursued%20a%20degree%20in%20his%2040s%2C%20but%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20land%20a%20job%20and%20ended%20up%20saddled%20with%20over%20%24100%2C000%20in%20student%20debt.%20The%20high%20cost%20of%20college%20is%20also%20a%20key%20factor%20as%20to%20why%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-