%3E%3Cp%3ELudlam-Raine%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealthy-oat-based-breakfast-recipes-for-fat-loss-muscle-gain-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoats%20for%20breakfast%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20chooses%20whole%20rolled%20oats%20rather%20than%20instant%2C%20which%20can%20be%20ultra-processed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20cooks%20her%20oatmeal%20then%20tops%20it%20with%20frozen%20berries%2C%20nuts%2C%20and%20seeds%2C%20so%20she's%20eating%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feating-30-plants-a-week-gut-health-easier-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediverse%20range%20of%20plants%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ludlam-Raine%20said.%20The%20aim%20is%20to%20add%20goodness%20into%20your%20meals%20when%20trying%20to%20eat%20more%20healthily%2C%20rather%20than%20cutting%20out%20foods%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20milk%20she%20uses%20to%20cook%20her%20oats%2C%20the%20least%20processed%20choice%20is%20usually%20dairy.%20However%2C%20Ludlam-Raine's%20son%20is%20allergic%20to%20dairy%2C%20so%20she%20doesn't%20use%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20foods%20have%20got%20a%20real%20place%20in%20people's%20lives%20who%20literally%20cannot%20consume%20certain%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20UPFs.%20%26quot%3BSo%20if%20my%20son%20didn't%20have%20UPF%20oat%20milk%2C%20he%20wouldn't%20be%20meeting%20his%20calcium%20and%20his%20iodine%20goals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20an%20example%20of%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20UPF%20in%20an%20otherwise%20whole-food%20meal%20being%20nothing%20to%20worry%20about%2C%20Ludlam-Raine%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20often%20has%20some%20Greek%20yogurt%20on%20the%20side%20for%20a%20protein%20boost%20too%2C%20which%20is%20a%20better%20choice%20than%20flavored%20yogurts%20which%20tend%20to%20be%20ultra-processed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Overnight%20oats.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%2