hen%20I%20looked%20at%20some%20of%20these%20ingredient%20lists.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20some%20brands%20of%20hummus%20may%20only%20include%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20one%20preservative%2C%20whereas%20others%20have%20many%20additives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20days%2C%20Ludlam-Raine%20has%20eggs%20on%20toast%20with%20a%20side%20salad%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ff7ca7e5-0d86-4e65-bdb6-6958cc177e35%5C%22%3ELook%20for%20snack%20bars%20that%20are%20non-UPF%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20an%20afternoon%20snack%2C%20Ludlam-Raine's%20choice%20depends%20on%20whether%20she%20is%20out%20or%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20looks%20for%20the%20least%20processed%20option%3A%20A%20chocolate%20bar%20would%20likely%20be%20UPF%2C%20while%20chocolate-covered%20almonds%20might%20also%20be%20UPF%20but%20would%20be%20more%20nutritious.%20So%20she%20would%20choose%20a%20snack%20bar%20that%20features%20whole%20foods%20mixed%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELudlam-Raine%2C%20who%20is%20based%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20likes%20brands%20including%20Nakd%20and%20Deliciously%20Ella.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223264%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chocolate%20bar.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f60d311851e792f0f0572f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222356%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChocolate%20can%20be%20ultra-processed.%3Cp%3ECapelle.r%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cc599221-5850-4125-b76c-273d479e7b85%5C%22%3ESpaghetti%20bolognese%20can%20be%20a%20non-UPF%20meal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20average%20dinner%20for%20Ludlam-Raine%20would%20be%20homemade%20Bolognese%20sauce%20made%20from%20lean%20ground%20beef%2C%20kidney%20beans%2C%20chopped%20tomatoes%2C%20and%20spices%2C%20served%20with%20spaghetti.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20make%20your%20Bolognese%20using%20a%20pre-made%20pasta%20sauce%2C%20however%2C%20it%20may%20contain%20UPF.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20these%20meals%20could%20be%20100%25%20non-UPF%2C%20actually%20there's%20a%20decision%20to%20be%20made%20on%20the%20oat%20milk%2C%20the%20bread%2C%20the%20pasta%20sauce%2C%26quot%3B%20Ludlam-Raine%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227726c5cd-56df-4933-ad6e-9d1f475e837d%5C%22%3EGreek%20yogurt%20and%20dark%20chocolate%20for%20dessert%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20satisfy%20her%20sweet%20tooth%20after%20dinner%2C%20Ludlam-Raine%20often%20eats%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-authentic-greek-yogurt-is-made-greece-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGreek%20yogurt%3C%2Fa%3E%20topped%20with%20a%20combination%20of%20dark%20chocolate%2C%20homemade%20granola%2C%20strawberries%2C%20or%20honey%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSugar%20isn't%20UPF%2C%20but%20because%20it's%20non-UPF%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20you%20can%20have%20as%20much%20of%20it%20as%20you%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20Ludlam-Raine%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20encourages%20people%20to%20eat%20unprocessed%20foods%20freely%20while%20being%20mindful%20of%20the%20sugar%20and%20fat%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20potato%20chips%2C%20for%20example%3A%20You%20can%20get%20non-UPF%20potato%20chips%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20you%20shouldn't%20watch%20your%20portion%20size%2C%20Ludlam-Raine%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20Ludlam-Raine%20thinks%20it's%20a%20mistake%20to%20consider%20only%20whether%20a%20food%20is%20a%20UPF%20when%20choosing%20what%20to%20eat%2C%20when%20there%20are%20many%20factors%20that%20determine%20how%20healthy%20something%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdietitian-wrote-book-ultra-processed-foods-eats-in-a-day-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720862222000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66914a8c5439fb59cebce025%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fww