idered%20with%20Naqshi%2C%20Saadi%2C%20and%20Zardozi%20techniques.%20The%20fully%20embroidered%20red%20shoulder%20dupatta%20added%20a%20dramatic%20touch%20to%20her%20bridal%20ensemble.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia's%20showing%20NATO%20its%20hand%20in%20the%20air%20war%20over%20Ukraine%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Russian%20Sukhoi%20Su-35S%20military%20fighter%20jet%20performs%20against%20a%20blue%20sky%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668fe28f724ee4419a5dba02%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20jets%20like%20this%20one%2C%20a%20Russian%20Sukhoi%20Su-35S%20military%20fighter%20jet%2C%20have%20been%20key%20elements%20of%20the%20air%20war%20over%20Ukraine%2C%20which%20is%20teaching%20the%20West%20a%20thing%20or%20two%20about%20how%20to%20fight%20Russia%20for%20the%20skies.%3Cp%3EPavel%20Pavlov%2FAnadolu%20Agency%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20alarm%20bells%20have%20been%20sounding%20throughout%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20warning%20loudly%20that%20if%20Kyiv%20falls%2C%20an%20emboldened%20Russia%20could%20set%20its%20sights%20on%20NATO%20next.%20In%20such%20a%20devastating%20fight%2C%20airpower%20and%20airspace%20control%20could%20be%20decisive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20air%20forces%20have%20underwhelmed%20over%20the%20past%202%20%C2%BD%20years%20of%20war%2C%20but%20they%20also%20have%20rapidly%20adapted%20and%20scored%20wins%20through%20tactics%20such%20as%20stand-off%20bombing%20and%20synchronized%20drone%20and%20missile%20barrages.%20Other%20elements%20of%20the%20aerospace%20forces%20have%20also%20effectively%20denied%20Ukraine%20the%20chance%20to%20shift%20the%20battlefield%20from%20the%20skies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20surprising%20they're%20adapting%20over%20time%20through%20trial%20and%20error%2C%26quot%3B%20Justin%20Bronk%2C%20an%20airpower%20expert%20at%20the%20UK's%20Royal%20United%20Services%20Institute%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20what%20this%20war%20has%20shown%2C%20to%20counter%20the%20Russians%2C%20NATO%20needs%20more%20air%20defenses%2C%20new%20ways%20of%20countering%20drones%2C%20and%20new%20basing%20concepts.%20Without%20these%2C%20the%20alliance%20could%20face%20a%20nastier%20fight%20should%20the%20worst%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20according%20to%20interviews%20with%20a%20dozen%20air-warfare%20experts%2C%20including%20former%20fighter%20pilots%20and%20current%20and%20former%20Western%20military%20commanders%20and%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20has%20underscored%20how%20some%20elements%20of%20modern%20air%20combat%20are%20radically%20changing.%20Advancing%20technologies%20have%20upended%20the%20operating%20environment%20in%20the%20skies%2C%20and%20extensive%20surface-to-air-missile%20networks%20are%20creating%20battlespaces%20almost%20impenetrable%20for%20older%20aircraft%20and%20still%20daunting%20for%20newer%2C%20more-advanced%20planes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERussia's%20air%20force%20hasn't%20done%20as%20well%20as%20expected%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20intense%20fighting%20in%20Ukraine%20has%20given%20the%20West%20a%20better%20picture%20of%20the%20Russian%20military's%20capabilities%20and%20revealed%20that%20many%20earlier%20assessments%20of%20its%20strength%20were%20overblown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-prized-s400-launchers-blasted-crimea-strike-ukraine-says-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evaunted%20Russian%20weapons%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20S-400%20air%20defenses%2C%20T-90M%20tanks%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bhypersonic%26quot%3B%20missiles%20deemed%20unstoppable%2C%20have%20not%20always%