s%2C%20particularly%20for%20strikes%20on%20cities%20and%20critical%20infrastructure.%20And%2C%20like%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20Russians%20have%20employed%20loitering%20munitions%20and%20cheap%20exploding%20first-person-view%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20threats%20collectively%20require%20layers%20of%20air%20defenses%2C%20electronic-warfare%20options%2C%20and%20more%20to%20defeat.%20As%20air-defense%20batteries%20fire%20away%20at%20higher-end%20threats%2C%20troops%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20conflict%20have%20taken%20to%20defending%20their%20trenches%20from%20the%20FPV%20drones%20with%20shotguns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20West%20needs%20more%20systems%20to%20counter%20such%20threats%2C%20including%20inexpensive%20options%20to%20down%20cheaper%20missiles%20and%20drones%20instead%20of%20using%20million-dollar%20interceptor%20missiles.%20One%20option%20could%20be%20the%20interceptor%20drones%20Ukraine%20is%20developing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFuture%20fights%20will%20strain%20air%20defenses%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20air-defense%20network%20is%20widely%20credited%20with%20stopping%20Russia%20from%20achieving%20greater%20gains%20and%20forcing%20it%20to%20fight%20a%20grinding%20ground%20war%20that%20has%20cost%20Russia%20absolutely%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-paying-severe-cost-casualties-new-offensive-us-intelligence-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estaggering%20losses%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20demand%20has%20been%20insatiable%2C%20and%20Valge%2C%20the%20Estonian%20air-force%20officer%2C%20said%20these%20defenses%20were%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20visible%20deficiency%26quot%3B%20in%20Western%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20agreed.%20A%20former%20Western%20air%20force%20intelligence%20officer%20described%20Europe's%20current%20missile%20defense%20network%20as%20%26quot%3Bkind%20of%20patchy%20with%20a%20few%20Patriots%20here%20and%20a%20few%20Patriots%20t