20of%20Union%20Temtory%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20(Second%20Amendment)%20Rules%2C%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20reads%20the%20notification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20amendments%20shall%20come%20into%20force%20on%20July%2012%2C%20the%20date%20of%20the%20publication%20in%20the%20Official%20Gazette%20-%20a%20move%20in%20anticipation%20of%20the%20speculated%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Transaction%20of%20Business%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Rules%2C%202019%20(hereinafter%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20principal%20rules)%2C%20some%20rules%20have%20been%20inserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20inserted%20sub-rule%20(2A)%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20proposal%20which%20requires%20previous%20concurrence%20of%20the%20Finance%20Department%20with%20regard%20to%20'Police'%2C%20'Public%20Order'%2C%20'All%20India%20Service'%20and%20'Anti%20Corruption%20Bureau'%20to%20exercise%20the%20discretion%20of%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20under%20the%20Act%20shall%20be%20concurred%20or%20rejected%20unless%20it%20has%20been%20placed%20before%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20through%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20principal%20rules%2C%20after%20rule%2042%2C%20rule%2042A%20has%20been%20inserted%20pointing%2C%20%26quot%3BDepartment%20of%20Law%2C%20Justice%20and%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20shall%20submit%20the%20proposal%20for%20appointment%20of%20Advocate-General%20and%20other%20Law%20Officers%20to%20assist%20the%20Advocate-General%20in%20the%20court%20proceedings%2C%20for%20approval%20of%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20through%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20and%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20inserted%20rule%2042B%2C%20%26quot%3BAny%20proposal%20regarding%20grant%20or%20refusal%20of%20prosecution%20sanction%20or%20filing%20of%20an%20appeal%20shall%20be%20placed%20before%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20through%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Law%2C%20Justice%20and%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20principal%20rules%2C%20in%20rule%2043%2C%20after%20the%20third%20proviso%2C%20the%20notification%20states%20that%20some%20provisos%20shall%20be%20inserted%2C%20focusing%20on%20matters%20connected%20with%20Prisons%2C%20Directorate%20of%20Prosecution%20and%20Forensic%20Science%20Laboratory%2C%20under%20which%20%26quot%3Bthe%20matters%20shall%20be%20submitted%20to%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20by%20Administrative%20Secretary%2C%20Home%20Department%20through%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProvided%20also%20that%20in%20respect%20of%20matters%20connected%20with%20posting%20and%20transfer%20of%20Administrative%20Secretaries%20and%20cadre%20posts%20of%20All%20India%20Services%20officers%2C%20the%20proposal%20shall%20be%20submitted%20to%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20by%20the%20Administrative%20Secretary%2C%20General%20Administration%20Department%20through%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20pertinent%20to%20mention%20that%20the%20principal%20rules%20were%20published%20in%20the%20Gazette%20of%20India%20dated%20August%2027%2C%202020%2C%20and%20subsequently%20amended%20on%20February%2028%2C%202024.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720850340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Feoarhd6s_amit-shah-1200_625x300_17_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhome-ministry-amends-j-k-reorganisation-act-boosts-powers-of-lt-governor-6095726%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20significant%20move%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20has%20amended%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganization%20Act%2C%202019%20enhanc