0Merchant's%20wedding%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20dressed%20in%20exquisite%20traditional%20attire.%20Deepika%20wore%20a%20sindoori%20red%20anarkali%20while%20Alia%20opted%20for%20a%20silk%20saree%20with%20a%20modern%20twist%2C%20both%20looking%20elegant%20and%20graceful%20at%20the%20event.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Can%20Become%20World's%202nd-Largest%20Economy%20By%202031%3A%20RBI%20Deputy%20Governor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20can%20become%20the%20second%20largest%20economy%20by%202031%20and%20the%20largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world%20by%202060%2C%20said%20Michael%20Debabrata%20Patra%2C%20Deputy%20Governor%2C%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20during%20a%20program%20at%20the%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%20National%20Academy%20of%20Administration%2C%20Mussoorie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20possible%20to%20imagine%20India%20striking%20out%20into%20the%20next%20decade%20to%20become%20the%20second%20largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world%20not%20by%202048%2C%20but%20by%202031%20and%20the%20largest%20economy%20of%20the%20world%20by%202060%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Patra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deputy%20governor%20stated%20during%20an%20event%20of%20the%20Mid-Career%20Training%20Programme%20for%20officials%20of%20the%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20on%20July%209%2C%20at%20the%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%20National%20Academy%20of%20Administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20called%20India's%20journey%20in%20economic%20development%20an%20eventful%20and%20arduous%20one%20and%20added%20that%20during%20the%20last%20financial%20year%202023-24%2C%20India%20became%20a%20USD%203.6%20trillion-dollar%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20had%20become%20a%20Rs%20295.4%20lakh%20crore%20or%20USD%203.6%20trillion%20dollars'%20economy%20at%20current%20exchange%20rates.%20At%20a%20per%20capita%20income%20of%20Rs%202%2C07%2C030%20or%20USD%202%2C500%2C%20India%20belongs%20in%20the%20lower%20middle-income%20group%20of%20countries.%20Reaching%20here%20has%20been%20an%20eventful%20and%20arduous%20journey%2C%20marked%20by%20what%20statisticians%20call%20'structural%20breaks%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Patra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deputy%20governor%20also%20added%20that%20if%20India%20wants%20to%20become%20a%20developed%20economy%20it%20will%20have%20to%20grow%20at%20a%20rate%20of%209.6%20per%20cent%20per%20annum%20for%20the%20next%20ten%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20India%20can%20grow%20at%20the%20rate%20of%209.6%20per%20cent%20per%20annum%20over%20the%20next%20ten%20years%2C%20it%20will%20break%20free%20of%20the%20shackles%20of%20the%20lower%20middle-income%20trap%20and%20become%20a%20developed%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Organisation%20for%20Economic%20Cooperation%20and%20Development%20(OECD)%20projects%20that%20in%20PPP%20(purchasing%20power%20parity)%20terms%2C%20India%20will%20overtake%20the%20US%20by%202048%20to%20become%20the%20second-largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20rising%20inflation%20in%20the%20Indian%20economy%2C%20the%20deputy%20governor%20stated%20that%20RBI%20is%20committed%20to%20aligning%20inflation%20with%20the%20target%20and%20the%20inflation%20will%20ease%20to%204.1%20per%20cent%20in%202025-26.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRBI%20has%20anchored%20expectations%20by%20remaining%20committed%20to%20aligning%20inflation%20with%20the%20target%20and%20regards%20the%20recent%20easing%20of%20price%20pressures%20as%20work%20in%20progress.%20It%20projects%20inflation%20to%20average%204.5%20per%20cent%20in%202024-25%20and%204.1%20per%20cent%20in%202025-26.%20The%20taming%20of%20inflation%20lays%20the%20foundations%20of%20sustained%20high%20growth%20in%20the%20future%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20deputy%20governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20shared%20that%20the%20Gross%20non-performing%20assets%20(GNPAs)%20in%20the%20banking%20system%20have%20steadily%20fallen%20from%20their%20peak%20in%20March%202018%20to%202.8%20per%20cent%20of%20total%20assets%20by%20March%202024.%20The%20adjusted%20for%20provisions%2C%20net%20NPAs%20are%20just%200.6%20per%20cent.%20The%20capital%20and%20liquidity%20buffers%20of%20the%20country%20are%20well%20above%20the%20regulatory%20norms.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720849740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Ffdntjp1o_rbi-deputy-governor-michael-debabrata-patra_625x300_13_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-can-become-worlds-2nd-largest-economy-by-2031-largest-by-2060-rbi-deputy-governor-6095683%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20can%20become%20the%20second%20largest%20economy%20by%202031%20and%20largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world%20by%202060%2C%20said%20Michael%20Debabrata%20Patra%2C%20Deputy%20Governor%2C%20RBI%20during%20a%20program%20at%20the%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%20National%20Academy%20of%20Administration%2C%20Mussoorie.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-can-become-worlds-2nd-largest-economy-by-2031-largest-by-2060-rbi-deputy-governor-6095683%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-can-become-worlds-2nd-largest-economy-by-2031-largest-by-2060-rbi-deputy-governor-6095683%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-can-become-worlds-2nd-largest-economy-by-2031-largest-by-2060-rbi-deputy-governor-6095683%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22John-Priya%20stun%20at%20Anant-Radhika's%20wedding%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%2