Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20India's%20exploration%20and%20production%20potential%20still%20lies%20untapped%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20find%20it%20strange%20that%20India%20is%20so%20heavily%20reliant%20on%20oil%20imports%20despite%20the%20abundant%20geological%20resources%20available%20to%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20sedimentary%20basins%20hold%20about%20651.8%20million%20tonnes%20of%20crude%20oil%20and%201138.6%20billion%20cubic%20meters%20of%20natural%20gas%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Puri%20said%20only%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20our%20sedimentary%20basin%20area%20is%20under%20exploration%2C%20which%20will%20rise%20to%2016%20per%20cent%20by%202024-end%20after%20the%20current%20bid%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20focus%20of%20our%20exploratory%20endeavours%20must%20pivot%20towards%20discovering%20'Yet%20to%20Find'%20resources%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20imports%20over%2085%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20crude%20oil%20needs.%20Crude%20oil%20is%20converted%20into%20fuels%20like%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20in%20refineries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20is%20doing%20its%20part%20to%20catalyse%20investments%20in%20E%26amp%3BP.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Petroleum%20and%20Natural%20Gas%20(MoPNG)%20has%20instituted%20sweeping%20reforms%2C%20empowering%20stakeholders%20to%20contribute%20to%20our%20nation's%20progress%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20%26quot%3BWe%20intend%20to%20increase%20India's%20exploration%20acreage%20to%201%20million%20sq.%20km.%20by%202030.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20since%20its%20inception%20in%202015%2C%20the%20Discovered%20Small%20Field%20(DSF)%20Policy%20has%20garnered%20investments%20of%20approximately%20USD%202%20billion%20and%20brought%20in%2029%20new%20players%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20opening%20up%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20no-go%20areas%20has%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20exploration%20activit