face.%20From%20then%20on%2C%20Nizam%E2%80%99s%20decided%20to%20serve%20%E2%80%98that%20dish%E2%80%99%20to%20everyone%20who%20came%20to%20eat%20%3Cem%3Ekebabs%20%3C%2Fem%3Eat%20the%20restaurant.%20The%20fact%20that%20it%20became%20a%20no-mess%20affair%20for%20anyone%20who%20wanted%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F340611%2Fhealthy-snack-brand-startup-open-secret-woman-entrepreneur-ahana-gautam-iit-bombay-harvard%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrab%20a%20quick%20snack%3C%2Fa%3E%20ensured%20its%20longevity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20for%20the%20story%20of%20the%20dish%E2%80%99s%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20hack%20of%20wrapping%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekebab%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20a%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Nizam%E2%80%99s%20also%20decided%20to%20tweak%20its%20strategy%20a%20little.%20The%20iron%20skewers%20that%20were%20in%20use%20were%20proving%20heavy%20and%20tedious%2C%20and%20so%2C%20these%20were%20swapped%20with%20substitutes%20made%20out%20of%20bamboo%20also%20called%20%3Cem%3Ekathi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(the%20Bengali%20word%20for%20stick).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkathi-roll-1720596960.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kathi%20roll%20is%20a%20popular%20snack%20eaten%20around%20India%20and%20it%20comes%20in%20many%20varieties%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkathi-roll-1720596960.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkathi-roll-1720596960-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkathi-roll-1720596960-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fka