rs%20can%20take%20a%20photo%20of%20the%20label%20and%20send%20it%20the%20number%20mentioned.%20You%20can%20then%20tear%20off%20the%20sticker%20and%20send%20the%20remaining%20two%20digits%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Prashant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20software%20analyses%20the%20image%20and%20confirms%20through%20the%20database%20whether%20the%20product%20is%20one%20of%20theirs%20or%20not.%20The%20entire%20code%20is%20matched%20with%20the%20additional%20two%20digits%20sent%20as%20a%20caption%20on%20WhatsApp.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrashant%20received%20the%20patent%20in%202021%20for%20the%20tamper%20preventive%20seal.%20It%20is%20single%20use%20and%20can%20be%20authenticated%20by%20customers%20through%20WhatsApp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20help%20the%20brand%20equity%20of%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355301%2Fgrowing-miyazaki-mango-on-terrace-udupi-home-gardener-joseph-lobo-chikoo-berries-jasmine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Devgad%20Hapus%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Omkar.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20also%20help%20the%20next%20generation%20continue%20farming%20as%20they%20can%20reap%20the%20fruits%20of%20their%20labour.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20hope%20that%20people%20will%20start%20recognising%20the%20true%20Devgad%20Hapus%20and%20consider%20the%20work%20that%20goes%20behind%20it.%20Our%20livelihoods%20are%20dependent%20on%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Santosh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20time%20you%20buy%20Devgad%20Alphonso%2C%20be%20sure%20to%20check%20the%20code!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20order%20these%20mangoes%20from%20the%20cooperative%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdevgadmango.com%2Fproduct%2Fmango%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Omkar%20Sap