n%20region.%20I%20specifically%20looked%20at%20Kashmir%20and%20Himachal%20and%20documented%20the%20entire%20construction%20process.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20background%2C%20Rahul%20got%20the%20idea%20of%20using%20his%20knowledge%20for%20the%20holistic%20sustainable%20development%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295759%2Fbest-himalayan-treks-in-autumn-valley-of-flowers-kashmir-great-lakes-plan-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHimalayan%20region.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20so%20many%20buildings%20that%20can%20be%20restored%20and%20preserved.%20These%20buildings%20were%20built%20almost%20100%20years%20ago%2C%20some%20even%2080%20or%20150%20years%20ago.%20These%20buildings%20cannot%20be%20built%20again.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20traditional%20houses%20in%20local%20villages%2C%20and%20the%20Britishers%20also%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20buildings%20in%20Himachal.%20Unfortunately%2C%20these%20buildings%20are%20now%20being%20abandoned%20or%20slowly%20going%20out%20of%20use.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-25-1720707759.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20homestay%20is%20made%20of%20mud%2C%20clay%20and%20reclaimed%20wood.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-25-1720707759.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-25-1720707759-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-25-1720707759-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-25-172070