%20instead%20store%20the%20excess%20energy%20and%20use%20it%20during%20non-generation%20hours%2C%20say%20during%20the%20nights%20and%20cloudy%20days.%20We%20have%20our%20own%20backup.%20As%20long%20as%20I%20am%20dependent%20on%20the%20grid%2C%20we%20are%20responsible%20for%20coal-backed%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20the%20major%20production%20of%20electricity%20is%20achieved%20through%20coal%20thermal%20power%20plants%20which%20is%20around%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coal.nic.in%2Fen%2Fmajor-statistics%2Fgeneration-of-thermal-power-from-raw-coal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E75%20percent%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20the%20total%20power%20generation.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20want%20to%20reduce%20your%20carbon%20footprint%2C%20you%20need%20to%20reduce%20your%20dependence%20on%20coal%20and%20thermal%20energy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBesides%2C%20if%20the%20grid%20in%20the%20net-metre%20system%20decides%20to%20shut%20down%2C%20my%20house%20will%20still%20be%20in%20darkness%20even%20though%20I%20am%20generating%20power%20from%20solar%20energy.%20The%20grid-backed%20system%20helps%20us%20create%20power%20backup%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESelf-dependent%20on%20energy%20%26amp%3B%20water%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20couple%20has%20not%20given%20up%20on%20their%20electricity%20metre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-1_11zon-1720701302.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20planned%20a%20grid%20backed%20solar%20photovoltaic%20(PV)%20system%20in%20the%20house%20with%20a%2015%20kWp%20capacity.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.th