d%20metre%20charge%20is%20about%20Rs%20500%20to%20700%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20setup%20cost%20the%20couple%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20and%20they%20believe%20they%20would%20get%20the%20return%20on%20investment%20within%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20limitations%20of%20the%20entire%20grid-backed%20setup%2C%20Shilpa%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COver%20the%20years%2C%20we%20developed%20a%20habit%20of%20running%20the%20washing%20machine%2C%20the%20mixer%2C%20water%20pumps%20only%20in%20the%20solar%20hours%20between%2010am%20to%205pm%20or%20it%20will%20lead%20to%20storage%20exhaustion.%20We%20run%20four%20ACs%20in%20the%20day%20and%20only%20two%20at%20night.%20You%20require%20this%20kind%20of%20discipline.%20But%20these%20are%20all%20matters%20of%20choice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-2-1720701386.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20harness%20solar%20energy%20to%20use%20energy%20consuming%20appliances%20like%20induction%2C%20microwave%2C%20washing%20machine.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-2-1720701386.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-2-1720701386-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-2-1720701386-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-2-1720701386-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-2-1720701386-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356504%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20couple%20harness%20solar%20energy%20to%20use%20energy%20consuming%20appliances%20like%20induction%2C%20microwave%2C%20washing%20machine.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20city%20dwellers%20are%20high-energy%20users.%20These%20days%2C%20people%20are%20switching%20to%20electric%20vehicles%20but%20in%20reality%2C%20how%20much%20carbon%20footprint%20will%20they%20really%20reduce%20if%20they%20continue%20to%20be%20dependent%20on%20grid%20power%3F%20Families%2C%20especially%20affluent%20ones%2C%20can%20adopt%20this%20approach%20to%20reduce%20their%20carbon%20footprint%20while%20enjoying%20power%2024%C3%977%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Suneet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20couple%20is%20also%20not%20dependent%20on%20the%20municipal%20water%20supply%20for%20their%20water%20needs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20already%20had%20a%20borewell.%20We%20took%20the%20opportunity%20of%20relying%20completely%20on%20ground%20water%20%E2%80%93%20from%20getting%20drinking%20water%20to%20watering%20our%20garden%20spread%20across%204%2C000%20sq%20feet%20area.%20We%20also%20direct%20excess%20water%20into%20the%20ground%20to%20recharge%20the%20aquifers.%20One%20good%20aspect%20of%20this%20was%20that%20our%20neighbours%20started%20getting%20sufficient%20water%20from%20their%20borewells%20even%20in%20the%20summers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Suneet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Shilpa%20and%20Suneet%2C%20the%20first%20biggest%20transformation%20with%20this%20setup%20was%20to%20have%20an%20uninterrupted%20power%20supply.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20live%20guilt-free.%20We%20do%20not%20require%20additional%20protection%20from%20probable%20fluctuations%20and%20spend%20on%20voltage%20stabilisers.%20Needless%20to%20say%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20worry%20about%20rising%20power%20costs%2C%20which%20is%20always%20a%20topic%20of%20discussion%20in%20our%20social%20gatherings.%20You%20can%20bring%20this%20change%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shilpa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Shilpa%20Kotwal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720706895000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D356491%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shilpa%20and%20Suneet%20Kotwal's%20home%20in%20Pune%20harvests%20solar%20power%20for%20uninterrupted%20electricity.%20Using%20solar%20panels%2C%20they%20run%20everything%20from%20a%20refrigerator%2C%20air%20conditioners%2C%20and%20other%20appliances%2C%20saving%2090%25%20on%20bills.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%2076-YO%20Teacher%20is%20Fighting%20Single-Handedly%20to%20Keep%20His%20Village%20School%20Open%2C%20All%20for%20Free%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20the%20most%20ordinary%20man%20you%20will%20ever%20interview%2C%E2%80%9D%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20things%20Dwijendra%20Nath%20Ghosh%2C%20a%20teacher%20in%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Purba%20Bardhman%20district%2C%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20might%20consider%20himself%20ordinary%2C%20what%20he%20has%20done%20for%20hundreds%20of%20children%20in%20his%20village%20of%20Basantpur%20is%20nothing%20short%20of%20extraordinary.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F297307%2Fkarnataka-retired-teacher-senior-citizen-helps-poor-students-with-scholarships%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretired%20government%20teacher%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%2076-year-old%20has%20a%20unique%20approach%20to%20retirement%20%E2%80%94%20he%20still%20teaches%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20Ghosh%E2%80%99s%20ageing%20smile%20has%20been%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20for%20the%20village%20children.%20He%20has%20been%20teaching%20and%20managing%20Basantapur%20Junior%20High%20School%2C%20keeping%20it%20from%20shutting%20down%2C%20all%20without%20charging%20a%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20does%20he%20do%20it%3F%20Smiling%20humbly%20through%20the%20wrinkles%20etched%20into%20his%20sun-tanned%20forehead%20by%20the%20Bengal%20sun%2C%20Ghosh%20shares%20his%20story%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECompassion%20like%20no%20other%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOften%20when%20we%20look%20for%20the%20source%20of%20inspiration%20and%20motivation%20in%20people%2C%20it%20is%20their%20own%20life%20experiences%20that%20push%20them%20to%20their%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20poor%20home.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20we%20struggled%20to%20find%20food.%20Getting%20an%20education%20when%20you%20come%20from%20an%20underprivileged%20and%20economically%20disadvantaged%20background%20is%20the%20biggest%20challenge.%20Turning%20your%20life%20around%20and%20achieving%20something%20that%20previous%20generations%20could%20not%20is%20very%20difficult%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20a%20financially%20unstable%20family%2C%20Ghosh%20understood%20the%20importance%20of%20helping%20others%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20came%20to%20education.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20work%20and%20struggled%20to%20get%20an%20education.%20If%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20work%20day%20and%20night%20to%20improve%20the%20system%20for%20the%20children%20of%20my%20village%2C%20then%20who%20will%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGhosh%20has%20a%20BEd%20degree%20and%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20English%20and%20political%20science.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20working%20as%20a%20teacher%20in%201975%20and%20retired%20in%202008%20as%20an%20assistant%20teacher%20at%20Jamalpur%20High%20School%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ghosh%20was%20fresh%20out%20of%20college%2C%20ready%20to%20work%2C%20he%20had%20opened%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F125632%2Fte