E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20a%20child%2C%20my%20mother%20would%20tell%20me%20stories%20about%20her%20dream%20of%20becoming%20an%20IAS%20officer.%20However%2C%20at%20that%20time%2C%20the%20environment%20was%20not%20conducive%20for%20women%20to%20pursue%20higher%20education%20and%20jobs.%20Opportunities%20were%20limited%2C%20and%20parents%20primarily%20focused%20on%20marrying%20off%20their%20daughters.%20She%20hoped%20to%20fulfil%20her%20dream%20through%20me%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20achieve%20this%20for%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20civil%20engineering%20degree%20from%20the%20DAV%20Institute%20of%20Engineering%20and%20Technology%20in%202013%2C%20Harsimran%20worked%20in%20the%20private%20sector%20for%20a%20year.%20In%202014%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20leave%20his%20job%20and%20prepare%20full-time%20for%20the%20UPSC-CSE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsimran%20cleared%20the%20Prelims%20on%20his%20first%20attempt%20but%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20clear%20the%20Mains.%20This%20pattern%20continued%20in%20his%20successive%20attempts%20in%202015%20and%202016.%20In%202017%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20clear%20the%20Mains%20but%20did%20not%20make%20it%20to%20the%20final%20list%20after%20the%20interview%20round.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20that%20time%2C%20I%20was%20unemployed%2C%20and%20I%20was%20not%20getting%20success%20in%20my%20attempts.%20I%20was%20disheartened%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20felt%20it%20was%20high%20time%20to%20work%20on%20his%20Plan%20B%20%E2%80%94%20securing%20a%20government%20position%20in%20the%20Punjab%20State%20Civil%20Services.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202017%2C%20I%20took%20up%20a%20job%20as%20an%20Inspector%20of%20Cooperative%20Society.%20This%20role%20allowed%20me%20to%20observe%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20Government%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level.%20It%20was%20an%20eye-opener%20for%20me.%20I%20realised%20that%20while%20civil%20services%20are%20often%20glamourised%2C%20the%20work%20of%20government%20officers%20is%20similar%20to%20any%20other%20job%2C%20with%20targets%20and%20goals%20to%20meet%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-3-1720617480.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harsimran%20secured%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%2016%20on%20his%20first%20attempt%20at%20UPSC-IFS.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-3-1720617480.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-3-1720617480-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-3-1720617480-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-3-1720617480-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-3-1720617480-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356340%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHarsimran%20secured%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%2016%20on%20his%20first%20attempt%20at%20UPSC-IFS.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20having%20a%20plan%20B%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20advise%20aspirants%20to%20spend%20years%20and%20years%20solely%20on%20exam%20preparation.%20This%20exam%20isn%E2%80%99t%20everything.%20It%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20diversify%20and%20not%20put%20all%20your%20eggs%20in%20one%20basket.%20That%20should%20be%20your%20initial%20approach.%20Many%20people%20waste%20years%20chasing%20glamour.%20Instead%2C%20dedicate%20two%20to%20three%20years%20of%20hard%20work%2C%20and%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20unable%20to%20clear%20it%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20perfectly%20fine%20to%20e