2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-7-1720534655.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ayan%20wanted%20to%20help%20farmers%20suffering%20from%20wild-life-related%20losses.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-7-1720534655.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-7-1720534655-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-7-1720534655-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-7-1720534655-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-7-1720534655-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356163%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAyan%20wanted%20to%20help%20farmers%20suffering%20from%20wild-life-related%20losses.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20engineer%E2%80%99s%20brain%20got%20into%20problem-solving%20mode%20and%20the%20idea%20of%20Katidhan%20was%20born.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20area%20needed%20more%20solutions%20that%20did%20not%20harm%20the%20animals.%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20newer%20projects%20to%20work%20on%20and%20this%20felt%20like%20a%20perfect%20opportunity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20Ayan%20set%20out%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20and%20collected%20a%20small%20team%20of%20scientists%20and%20engineers%20to%20develop%20an%20animal-friendly%20resolution.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20more%20I%20spoke%20to%20the%20farmers%20in%20different%20regions%20during%20the%20initial%20stages%20of%20the%20project%2C%20the%20more%20I%20realised%20how%20small-scale%20farmers%20suffer%20more%20due%20to%20animal%20