er-cyclone-india-water-warriors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereviving%20water%20bodies%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20well%20be%20a%20gold%20standard%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20rural%20landscape%20that%20is%20struggling%20with%20water%20problems%20in%20the%20face%20of%20changing%20climate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAs%20precious%20as%20gold%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nursery%20rhymes%20we%20grew%20up%20hearing%20are%20rooted%20in%20our%20memories.%20Likewise%20for%20Tiwari%20and%20the%20children%20of%20his%20village%3B%20albeit%20the%20rhymes%20were%20slightly%20different.%20Veering%20away%20from%20the%20popular%20ones%2C%20these%20verses%20emphasised%20the%20crucial%20importance%20of%20water%20in%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDhaura%20tera%20paanee%20gajab%20kari%20jae%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3Egagaree%20(matakee)%20na%20phootai%2C%20khasam%20(pati)%20maree%20jae.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETranslating%20these%20lines%2C%20and%20underscoring%20their%20meaning%2C%20Tiwari%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20%5Bthe%20rhyme%5D%20originated%20centuries%20ago%20when%20the%20women%20of%20the%20village%20would%20walk%20for%20miles%20to%20fetch%20water%20from%20a%20certain%20pond.%20The%20water%20was%20considered%20so%20prized%20and%20expensive%20that%20the%20women%20would%20often%20pray%20to%20God%20to%20not%20let%20the%20%3Cem%3Ematkas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(mud%20pots)%20crack%20and%20tell%20Him%20that%20He%20could%20take%20away%20their%20husbands%20instead.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rhyme%2C%20though%20morbid%2C%20encapsulates%20the%20pedestal%20on%20which%20water%20was%20put%20in%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages--1720083198.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ra