istrict-gets-aid-water-bodies-desilted%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esevere%20drought%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20sharply%20increased%20in%20the%20last%2030%20years%20in%20Bundelkhand.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20records%20from%20the%20Government%20show%20a%20spell%20of%20one%20drought%20in%2016%20years%20during%20the%2018th%20and%2019th%20centuries%20in%20Bundelkhand.%20From%201968%20to%201992%2C%20the%20region%20saw%20a%20drought%20every%20five%20years.%20However%20in%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20the%20region%20has%20already%20suffered%20seven%20years%20of%20drought%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20light%20of%20this%2C%20conserving%20water%20was%20second%20nature%20for%20Tiwari.%20But%20these%20ideals%20tended%20to%20get%20blurred%20when%20he%20moved%20to%20Allahabad%20for%20further%20studies%20in%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bathroom%20of%20his%20own%3B%20showers%20for%20baths%3B%20unlimited%20water%20supply%20and%20no%20one%20having%20to%20walk%20miles%20to%20fetch%20it%2C%20introduced%20Tiwari%20to%20a%20whole%20new%20world.%20He%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20believe%20his%20luck.%20But%20while%20the%20initial%20weeks%20of%20this%20%E2%80%9Cfantasy%20life%E2%80%9D%20pushed%20all%20thoughts%20of%20water%20scarcity%20out%20of%20his%20mind%2C%20weekend%20visits%20back%20home%20did%20not%20allow%20him%20to%20forget%20about%20his%20village%E2%80%99s%20woes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20began%20to%20draw%20parallels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-1-1720083334.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Bajrang%20Sagar%20pond%20that%20Rambabu%20Tiwari%20has%20helped%20revive%20was%20previously%20barren%20and%20filled%20with%20silt%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-vil