d%20from%20Allahabad%20where%20he%20was%20studying%2C%20and%20mobilise%20the%20people%20of%20his%20village%20to%20desilt%20the%20ponds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20observed%20that%20the%20ponds%20had%20a%20great%20capacity%2C%20but%20because%20they%20were%20choked%20with%20silt%2C%20their%20water%20accumulation%20capacity%20had%20gone%20down.%20So%2C%20even%20during%20the%20monsoons%2C%20the%20entire%20pond%20could%20not%20be%20filled.%20Come%20January%20every%20year%2C%20we%20faced%20water%20shortage%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20story%20of%20the%20first%20pond%20of%20focus%20%E2%80%98Bajrang%20Sagar%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20pond%20with%20an%2011%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20traditional%20unit%20to%20measure%20the%20area%20of%20a%20plot%20of%20land%3B%201%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3D%20%E2%85%93%20to%201%20acre)%20capacity%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20one%20of%20the%20major%20water%20bodies%20in%20the%20village%20and%20situated%20right%20near%20Hanuman%20Mandir.%20When%20I%20would%20call%20people%20to%20desilt%20the%20pond%20initially%2C%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20ready.%20So%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20keep%20prayers%20at%20the%20%3Cem%3Emandir%20%3C%2Fem%3E(temple)%20and%20people%20started%20coming%20in%20hordes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-4-1720083584.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Desilting%20the%20Bajrang%20Sagar%20pond%20took%20a%20total%20of%20eight%20weeks%20with%20the%20villagers%20putting%20in%2024%20hours%20of%20work%20each%20week%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-4-1720083584.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F0