%20do%20jobs%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20I%20was%20more%20inclined%20to%20do%20business%20as%20jobs%20in%20the%20tech%20field%20are%20at%20constant%20threat%20of%20recession%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20third%20year%20of%20his%20college%2C%20Harsh%20started%20looking%20for%20business%20opportunities%20across%20various%20industries.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20my%20parents%20were%20against%20this%20idea.%20They%20wanted%20me%20to%20focus%20completely%20on%20my%20studies%20first.%20I%20did%20not%20quit%20on%20that%20idea%20but%20instead%20started%20exploring%20business%20opportunities%20in%20agriculture%20so%20that%20my%20parents%20understand%20the%20work%20and%20did%20not%20object%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20while%20pursuing%20his%20higher%20education%20in%20computer%20science%20in%20Navi%20Mumbai%2C%20Harsh%20started%20looking%20for%20new%20technologies%20and%20methods%20of%20farming.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20started%20researching%2C%20I%20came%20across%20new%20crops%20like%20dragon%20fruits%2C%20sandalwood%2C%20and%20saffron%20farming.%20Unlike%20other%20crops%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20would%20be%20able%20to%20easily%20tap%20into%20the%20market%20with%20saffron%20as%20it%20is%20the%20most%20expensive%20spice%20in%20the%20world.%20This%20would%20save%20me%20time%20and%20energy%20to%20completely%20focus%20on%20the%20production%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaffron-farming-1720186205.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harsh%20cultivates%20saffron%20in%20a%20controlled%20environment%20using%20the%20aeroponics%20technique%20in%20a%2015x15%20room.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaffron-farming-1720186205.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-me